sentences.english: Regular review ca strong make our new knowledge perma strongnent.
sentences.chinese: 按期複習能幫手波動新知識。

sentences.english: Loan sharks often use gangsters to put the screws on people who do not meet their payment deadlines.
sentences.chinese: 高利貸者常常利用流氓對不按期還錢的人們進行威脅。

sentences.english: They work non-stop to finish the audit on time.
sentences.chinese: 他們不停地工作以按期完成審計工作。

sentences.english: Ensure house is tidy and scheduled chores/jobs are completed.
sentences.chinese: 將屋子打掃乾淨，並確保日常雜務都已按期完成。

sentences.english: Studentswho do not complete internship or fail to meet internship requirements will notbe awarded credit.
sentences.chinese: 不能按期完成實習或實習考覈未達標者不能授予學分。

sentences.english: An effective democracy holds regular elections.
sentences.chinese: 有效的民主軌制按期舉辦選舉。

sentences.english: We should give this project every support so that it may be completed on schedule.
sentences.chinese: 對該項工程應予大力支持，俾能按期完成。

sentences.english: This won't stop us from starting the work on the project on time.
sentences.chinese: 這不妨礙我們按期動工。

sentences.english: Second, you may find the person can help you to better meet your deadline.
sentences.chinese: 第二，你會找到能幫你更好按期完成工作的人。

sentences.english: The enterprise or institution must complete the task within the specified period of time.
sentences.chinese: 被限期治理的企業事業單位必須按期完成治理任務。

sentences.english: We got the project done on schedule.
sentences.chinese: 我們按期完成了這個項目。

sentences.english: I was held up on the way and so I was late.
sentences.chinese: 途中遇事耽擱，故未能按期到達。

sentences.english: The emperors periodically toured the four peaks in order to take stock of their realm.
sentences.chinese: 徽孥按期巡遊四山去啃扉其範圍。
